################################################################################
# FIXED-WING ENVELOPE AND ENERGY CONTROL
################################################################################

# qtail11-qtail14 truth showed that px4xplane body-axis pitot (-Z) is positive
# and close to X-Plane true airspeed in FW mode. Use it for transition gating
# and TECS. Do not make the virtual SITL pitot a prearm hardware requirement:
# commander can run before the simulator stream and airspeed_selector warm up.
